<template>
  <b-tr>
    <b-td>{{ name }} </b-td>
    <b-td>{{ sidoname }} {{ dong }} {{ jibun }} </b-td>
    <b-td>{{ floor }}ì¸µ</b-td>
    <b-td>{{ type }} </b-td>
    <b-td>{{ wal }} </b-td>
    <b-td>{{ jeon }} </b-td>
    <b-td>
      <b-button class="mb-2">
        <b-icon icon="trash-fill" aria-hidden="true" @click="deleteLikeHouse"> </b-icon>
      </b-button>
      <!-- <b-button> <b-icon icon="trash-fill" aria-hidden="true"></b-icon> </b-button -->
    </b-td>
  </b-tr>
</template>

<script>
import { apiInstance } from "@/api/index.js";
const http = apiInstance();
export default {
  name: "LikeListItem",
  components: {},
  props: {
    id: String,
    lno: Number,
    sidoname: String,
    name: String,
    dong: String,
    jibun: String,
    type: String,
    wal: Number,
    jeon: Number,
    floor: String,
  },
  data() {
    return {
      likeHouse: {
        id: "",
        name: "",
        dong: "",
        jibun: "",
        type: "",
        wal: 0,
        jeon: 0,
        floor: "",
      },
    };
  },
  created() {},

  methods: {
    deleteLikeHouse() {
      this.likeHouse = {
        id: this.id,
        name: this.name,
        dong: this.dong,
        jibun: this.jibun,
        type: this.jibun,
        wal: this.wal,
        jeon: this.jeon,
        floor: this.floor,
      };
      http
        .post(`/like/delete`, JSON.stringify(this.likeHouse))
        .then((response) => {
          console.log(response);
        })
        .catch((error) => {
          console.log(error);
        });
    },
  },
};
</script>

<style scoped></style>
